Hello <%= @user.first_name %>,

Someone from <%= @organisation.name %> has added you to their team on digitalsocial.eu

<% if @user.organisation_memberships.count == 1 %>
Click the link below to sign in and set your password.
<%= edit_password_url(@user, :reset_password_token => @user.reset_password_token, :new => 1) %>
<% else %>
Click below to log in to the <%= @organisation.name %> dashboard.
<%= dashboard_url(org_id: @organisation.guid) %>
<% end %>

